==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/pəˈteɪtəʊ/}}

===Etymology===
From Taino [[batata]] via Spanish [[patata]].

===Noun===
'''potato''' (''plural:'' '''[[potatoes]]''')

#A plant [[tuber]], ''[[Solanum tuberosum]]'', often eaten as a starchy vegetable, particularly in the [[Americas]] and [[Europe]]. 

